    {
      "id": "1924750c-f3ba-80ab-8082-c221f0222f6a",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors use a recommender system to provide automated feedback after summative assessment. The feedback is given in the form of a set of questions that would be benefical for the student in question.b This requires, first, the construction of a knowledge model of the learner and second the identification of the gaps in that knowledge. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1924750c-f3ba-80ab-8082-c221f0222f6a",
        "parent": {
