    {
      "id": "1934750c-f3ba-8018-8356-c1dda1a844b7",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors do recommendations using multiple popular algorithms. Results on secondary education level show that the recommendations can be done reasonably well without a lot of computational complexity.  ",
